  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase materials, construct boats and yachts, and fulfill customer orders. Start small with humble fishing boats and work your way up to sleek, high-performance racing yachts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy boat building materials</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your knowledge in shipbuilding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fulfill your customers' orders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade on the islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the inhabitants of neighboring islands and carry out their orders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the hidden treasures </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail to distant islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the storyline that will help you learn Andy's story.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase materials, construct boats and yachts, and fulfill customer orders. Start small with humble fishing boats and work your way up to sleek, high-performance racing yachts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy boat building materials</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your knowledge in shipbuilding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fulfill your customers' orders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade on the islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the inhabitants of neighboring islands and carry out their orders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the hidden treasures </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail to distant islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the storyline that will help you learn Andy's story.</p></li></ul>",
